owth}} ({{TRM}})\n* {{p|Piplup}} ({{OP|Dawn|Piplup}})\n* {{p|Aipom}} ({{OP|Ash|Aipom}})\n* {{p|Staravia}} ({{OP|Ash|Staravia}})\n* {{p|Turtwig}} ({{OP|Ash|Turtwig}})\n* {{p|Buneary}} ({{OP|Dawn|Buneary}})\n* {{p|Pachirisu}} ({{OP|Dawn|Pachirisu}})\n* {{p|Buizel}} ({{OP|Dawn|Buizel}})\n* {{p|Sudowoodo}} ({{OP|Brock|Sudowoodo}})\n* {{p|Croagunk}} ({{OP|Brock|Croagunk}})\n* {{p|Happiny}} ({{OP|Brock|Happiny}})\n* {{p|Seviper}} ({{OP|Jessie|Seviper}})\n* {{p|Dustox}} ({{OP|Jessie|Dustox}})\n* {{p|Elekid}} ({{OP|Paul|Elekid}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Chimchar}} ({{OP|Paul|Chimchar}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Starly}} ([[Paul]]'s; flashback)\n* {{p|Glameow}} ({{OP|Zoey|Glameow}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Shellos}} ({{OP|Zoey|Shellos}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Glameow}} ({{OP|Johanna|Glameow}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Mesprit}} ({{DL|Lake guardians (anime)|Mesprit|anime}}; spirit; flashback)\n* {{p|Cranidos}} ({{OP|Roark|Cranidos}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Rampardos}} ({{OP|Roark|Rampardos}}; flashback)\n* {{p|Onix}} ([[Roark]]'s; flashback)\n* {{p|Roserade}} ([[Gardenia]]'s; flashback)\n* {{p|Nuzleaf}} ({{OBP|Yoko|DP037}}'s; flashback)\n* {{p|Linoone}}\n\n==Trivia==\n* [[Aim to Be a Pokémon Master]] 2001, instrumental versions of [[By Your Side ~Hikari's Theme~]] and [[Advance Adventure]], and [[Pokémon Symphonic Medley]] are used as background music.\n* This is the second clip episode in the [[Pokémon anime]]'s history, the first being [[AG120]]. Like its predecessor, it was skipped in the [[dub]]. This was also the first episode to be skipped by [[The Pokémon Company International]].\n* [[Professor Oak's Big Pokémon Encyclopedia]]: {{p|Torterra}}\n** Pokémon senryū: ドダイトス\u3000こうらはみどりの\u3000どだいです ''Dodaitosu, kōra wa midori no, dodai desu.''\n* [[Jessie's Wobbuffet]] doesn't appear in this episode.\n\n===Dub edits===\n* This episode was skipped in the dub. [[AG120]] and [[DP120]], both also clip shows, were skipped in the dub as well.\n\n==In other languages==\nAs most non-Japanese versions of the anime are based on the American dub, this episode has not aired anywhere outside of Japan.\n\n{{-}}\n{{EpicodePrevNext|\nprevcode=DP047 |\nprevtitle=Sandshrew's Locker! |\nnextcode=DP049 |\nnexttitle=Dawn's Early Night|\nseries=Diamond & Pearl series |\ncolorscheme=Sinnoh}}\n{{Project Anime notice}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:0514}}\n[[Category:Diamond & Pearl series episodes|048]]\n[[Category:Clip episodes]]\n[[Category:Undubbed episodes]]\n\n[[de:Satoshi to Hikari! Aratanaru Bōken ni Mukatte!!]]\n[[es:EP517]]\n[[fr:DP048]]\n[[it:DP048]]\n[[ja:DP編第48話]]\n[[zh:精灵宝可梦 钻石＆珍珠 总集篇 第1集]]"}